OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FGhanian footballer and former Arsenal
OL,8,Fplayer denies all the charges and is
OL,9,Fexpected to go to trial in January
OL,10,F2027, ITV News' Sports Editor Steve
OL,11,FScott reports
OL,13,FThe Football Association will not
OL,14,Fissue guidance to the England squad
OL,15,Fover whether to shake hands with the
OL,16,FGhanaian player Thomas Partey, who has
OL,17,Fbeen charged with seven counts of
OL,18,Frape, ITV News understands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
