OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FEngland are due to meet Ghana in their
OL,8,Fsecond World Cup match in Boston at
OL,9,F9pm BST on Tuesday.
OL,11,FPartey, who is vice-captain of Ghana,
OL,12,Fwas first charged with five counts of
OL,13,Frape and one count of sexual assault
OL,14,Fin July 2025, and two more counts of
OL,15,Frape in February this year.
OL,17,FThe allegations, all of which are from
OL,18,Fthe UK, date back to 2020, 2021 and
OL,19,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
