OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FPartey denies all the charges and is
OL,13,Fexpected to go to trial at Southwark
OL,14,Fcrown court in January 2027.
OL,16,FThe former Arsenal midfielder was
OL,17,Fforced to miss Ghana's opening game
OL,18,Fagainst Panama after he was denied
OL,19,Fentry to Canada over the charges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
