OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782159506
OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FPartey unsuccessfully appealed the
OL,8,Fdecision to reject his visa
OL,9,Fapplication. However, he is available
OL,10,Fto play against England in Boston
OL,11,Fbecause the US has granted him a visa.
OL,13,FThe FA has not issued any instructions
OL,14,Fon how England players should act when
OL,15,Fboth sides shake hands ahead of kick-
OL,16,Foff.
OL,18,FFA chief executive Mark Bullingham
OL,19,Fsaid England have the best chance of
OL,20,Fwinning the World Cup if they're
OL,21,Fallowed to "focus on football".
