OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FGhana's head coach, Carlos Queiroz, a
OL,8,Fformer assistant of Sir Alex Ferguson
OL,9,Fat Manchester United, has maintained
OL,10,Fhis player should be regarded as
OL,11,Finnocent unless proven guilty.
OL,13,F"Let events run their normal course,
OL,14,Flet the river flow and one day, when
OL,15,Fthe river meets the ocean, we will
OL,16,Ffind the truth," he has said.
OL,18,FEngland's Bukayo Saka and Declan Rice
OL,19,Fwere both previously teammates with
OL,20,FPartey at Arsenal.
