OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FPartey is not the only player in the
OL,8,FWorld Cup with charges against him, as
OL,9,FMorocco's captain was told he will
OL,10,Fstand trial for rape by a French
OL,11,Fappeals court on Friday.
OL,13,FAchraf Hakimi, who plays for Paris
OL,14,FSaint-Germain, was accused of raping a
OL,15,F24-year-old woman at his home in the
OL,16,FFrench capital in 2023, which he
OL,17,Fdenies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
