PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782159506
OL,3,CWill England players shake Thomas
OL,4,CPartey's hand at their match against
OL,5,CGhana?
OL,7,FShortly after the court of appeal
OL,8,Fdelivered its ruling, Hakimi wrote on
OL,9,FX that he had been "waiting for this
OL,10,Ftrial since day one. At last, I'll be
OL,11,Fable to speak." A date has not been
OL,12,Fannounced for trial.
